token_lists.title: Hyperdimensional/Non Sequiturs
token_lists.description: A series derived from my personal collection of glitch artifacts that explore technical processes of animation and collage as well as psychedelic, kinesthetic impressions upon the body. Each artifact is produced via unique forms of creative coding and/or special effects and combines movement from two seemingly different material objects to produce difference, uncertainty, and the new.
